-- Madrid Region Cuts Public Wages, Raises Taxes, Cinco Dias Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-06-08T05:43:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-08/madrid-region-cuts-public-wages-raises-taxes-cinco-dias-says.html
The region of  Madrid  presented
additional austerity measures, including cutting public wages by
3.3 percent to 10 percent, raising 74 taxes and public tariffs
and introducing tolls on free highways,  Cinco Dias  reported,
citing Madrid government officials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
